I was raised and educated by my Father the Evil Necromancier; Conspirutus Von Trox.<br>
I had not the intelligence (<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) to become an Necromancier, but I had the strenght to become a Shadow Knight.<br>
