Years went by and we where a happy Evil family.<br>
<br>
Until this really, really good Paladin found out where the Von Trox home castle was.......<br>
<br>
Things changed then......<br>
<br>
A large army of faulty paladin's sieged our Castle...<br>
we, the Von Trox family fought untill the ground was red of blood and guts.....Allas, they where many, a 100, a 1000, maybe more, we where only 10 (<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ), after they broke a wall, they rushed in like roaches clensing our foul, but Evil castle.......<br>
<br>
I was trapped by a dozen of these paladins, i hated them, being so goood ! And i started killing them, one by one, i slashed body's, arm's, legg's and ofcourse heads.........<br>
When they didn't say their prayer's anymore and i cleaned my bloody 2h sword with their tunic's i heared an awfull scream.....<br>
<br>
FATHER, FATHER, FATHER ................!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br>
<br>
I rushed up to the main tower as fast as i could...Only to see this really, really good paladin standing in front of the decapitated body of my beloved Evil father... <br>
<br>
Rage came up, as i saw this picture burned into my eyes.<br>
when i regained my self again, i had a heart in my hand... I looked around, only to see this really, really dead paladin his eyes wide open with a gap in his armor, blood all over him......<br>
<br>
I crushed the heart in my hand, toke my 2h sword and left......searching...., searching for more hearts to crush......<br>
